        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A house is built by wisdom and becomes strong through good sense. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A house is built by wisdom and becomes strong through good sense."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Through knowledge its rooms are filled with all sorts of precious riches and valuables. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The wise are mightier than the strong, and those with knowledge grow stronger and stronger. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The wise are mightier than the strong, and those with knowledge grow stronger and stronger."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "So don’t go to war without wise guidance; victory depends on having many advisers. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "So don’t go to war without wise guidance; victory depends on having many advisers."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Wisdom is too lofty for fools. Among leaders at the city gate, they have nothing to say. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Wisdom is too lofty for fools. Among leaders at the city gate, they have nothing to say."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A person who plans evil will get a reputation as a troublemaker. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A person who plans evil will get a reputation as a troublemaker."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The schemes of a fool are sinful; everyone detests a mocker. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The schemes of a fool are sinful; everyone detests a mocker."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
